er the Ukraine war. Russia vehemently condemned the seizure as illegal, bordering on 'international terrorism,' and vowed to protect its shipping. This action is part of a wider Western effort to curb Russia's 'shadow fleet' used to circumvent sanctions.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/international-terrorism-russia-slams-frances-seizure-of-russian-linked-tanker-terms-it-illegal/articleshow/131439405.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/europe/international-terrorism-russia-slams-frances-seizure-of-russian-linked-tanker-terms-it-illegal/articleshow/131439405.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-01T15:17:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131439451,imgsize-470219.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Challenge cup-winning coach and broadcaster John Kear dies aged 71 as tributes pour in]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131439142.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Rugby league mourns the loss of influential figure John Kear, who passed away at 71. Renowned for his tactical acumen and ability to inspire underdogs, Kear's four-decade career as a coach, mentor, and broadcaster earned him widespread respect. His legacy includes transforming struggling teams and fostering a deep love for the sport.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/challenge-cup-winning-coach-and-broadcaster-john-kear-dies-aged-71-as-tributes-pour-in/articleshow/131439142.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/challenge-cup-winning-coach-and-broadcaster-john-kear-dies-aged-71-as-tributes-pour-in/articleshow/131439142.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-01T15:08:52+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.